| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4130 — Recovery Inhibition (alphalocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b6365c73-38c6-5297-986b-63b014695611"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
